      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/european-stocks-rise-after-holiday-with-miners-energy-leading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员重新评估利率走势，欧洲股市回吐早前涨幅。与此同时，随着商品股上涨，英国富时 100 指数创下收盘新高。]]></description>
